    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lights, camera, action!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221830/extras/ddba0ad9bef529511a70afc0156a586a.avif?t=1758172342\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Destino Indomable, you're the hot new actress tasked with playing the main character in a telenovela! This is a wild visual novel inspired by the craziest Latin soap operas, filled with humor, drama, romance, horses, handsome men, Spanglish and slaps! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your own character and complete 5 thrilling telenovela episodes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221830/extras/355a13f39e786b46ab4066b7dffa6713.avif?t=1758172342\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All your choices will impact the story, how the characters treat you and even the ratings for the show!  You may even discover gossip for the hottest cast members!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mysteries in the Montenegro de la Vega Hacienda, get entangled in a crazy love triangle and drive the crowd crazy with the wildest show you can come up with! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are you ready to take your part?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221830/extras/9559a284b44cb42826e6dbae0e45d784.avif?t=1758172342\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Telenovela themed visual novel</strong>: We're bringing all the magic and surreal elements from Latin telenovelas to the VN Genre! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character popularity system</strong>: Depending on your actions, some characters may see more screen time. The more a character appears, the more the audience will love them! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create the perfect lead actress</strong>: Play with your clothes, hairstyle, colors, accessories, body types and more! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Five romance paths</strong>: What's a good telenovela without some romance? Each character offers a plotline to discover. You'll learn a different piece of the mystery by seeing each of them! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different endings</strong>: Your choices through the telenovela will shape the story, culminating in more than 5 vastly different endings. Heroes become villains, villains become heroes, people return from the death... it's a telenovela, anything goes! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 15 hours of story</strong>: This game is very vast and filled with little details to uncover. You may find a secret or two that you wouldn't in a different playthrough.</p></li></ul>",
